title: Swype [Arcade, Eng, 2018]
description:
Swipe is a real test of your speed and reaction.
Clear obstacles, collect stars, buy new character icons,
and become a leader in the world table of records.

How to play?
Use the mouse to fly around the rotating obstacles.
Press the mouse button with upward movement for acceleration, and downward movement for deceleration.
Collect stars so you can buy a new look for your character.

System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 1 GHz
RAM: 128 mb
VRAM: 64 mb
HDD: 71 mb
